Source: rdkit
Section: science
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13),
               libboost-dev,
               librdkit-dev (>= 202303.3),
               librdkit-dev (<< 202303.4~),
               postgresql-server-dev-all
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/rdkit/rdkit

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-rdkit
Section: database
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         postgresql-PGVERSION
Description: RDKit cartridge for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 RDKit adds cheminformatics data types, operators, and functions to PostgreSQL.
 .
 This Pigsty package fills PostgreSQL 17-18 gaps on Debian 12 and Ubuntu 22.04
 while using the RDKit runtime supplied by PGDG.
